OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FKirsty Young opens up about
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchronic pain diagnosis     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Broadcaster Kirsty Young has spoken    
OL,6, about her "awful" experience of chronic
OL,7, pain, which led her to take a four-year
OL,8, break from presenting.                 
OL,10,FYoung stepped down as host of Desert   
OL,11,FIsland Discs in 2018 as a result of    
OL,12,Ffibromyalgia and rheumatoid arthritis. 
OL,14,FAfter returning to the airwaves earlier
OL,15,Fthis year, she has now gone back to the
OL,16,FBBC Radio 4 show for its Christmas Day 
OL,17,Fepisode - this time as the interviewee.
OL,19,FChronic pain "grinds you away", she    
OL,20,Ftold her successor Lauren Laverne.     
